:Namespace Prepl
‚ćĚ Prepl: A programmable REPL server for Dyalog APL
‚ćĚ Inspired by Clojure's prepl
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Protocol (pure APLAN):
‚ćĚ   Input:  APL expression, newline-terminated
‚ćĚ   Output: APLAN namespace, newline-terminated:
‚ćĚ     (tag: 'ret' ‚čĄ val: 1 2 3)         ‚ÄĒ return value
‚ćĚ     (tag: 'ret')                        ‚ÄĒ no displayable result (shy/void)
‚ćĚ     (tag: 'err' ‚čĄ en: 11 ‚čĄ message: 'DOMAIN ERROR' ‚čĄ dm: (...))
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Usage:
‚ćĚ   2 ‚éēFIX 'file:///path/to/Prepl.apln'
‚ćĚ   Prepl.Start 4200          ‚ćĚ blocking
‚ćĚ   Prepl.LoadConga            ‚ćĚ pre-load on main thread (‚éēCY needs thread 0)
‚ćĚ   tid‚ÜźPrepl.Start&4200      ‚ćĚ on new thread (& is an operator: f&arg)
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Loads Conga from workspace if needed.

    ‚éēIO‚Üź1

    LDRC‚Üź‚ć¨           ‚ćĚ Conga instance (set by LoadConga)
    _stop‚Üź0          ‚ćĚ Stop flag
    _buf‚Üź''          ‚ćĚ Receive buffer (v1: single connection)

    ‚ćĚ ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Server Lifecycle ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ

    ‚ąá LoadConga
    ‚ćĚ Load and initialize Conga. Copies from ws if not already present.
      :If 9‚Č†‚Ćä#.‚éēNC'Conga'
          'Conga'#.‚éēCY'conga'
      :EndIf
      LDRC‚Üź#.Conga.Init'prepl'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Start port;z
      _stop‚Üź0
      _buf‚Üź''
      :If ‚ć¨‚Č°LDRC ‚čĄ LoadConga ‚čĄ :EndIf   ‚ćĚ Skip if pre-loaded by bootstrap
      :Trap 0 ‚čĄ {}LDRC.Close'prepl' ‚čĄ :EndTrap
      z‚ÜźLDRC.Srv'prepl' '' port 'Raw' 4096
      :If 0‚Č†‚äÉz
          ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl: failed to start on port ',‚ćēport
          :Return
      :EndIf
      ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl listening on port ',‚ćēport
      Loop
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Stop
      _stop‚Üź1
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá Loop;wres;rc;obj;evt;data
      :While ~_stop
          wres‚ÜźLDRC.Wait'prepl' 5000
          :If 0‚Č†1‚äÉwres
              :If 100‚Č°1‚äÉwres ‚čĄ :Continue ‚čĄ :EndIf   ‚ćĚ Timeout (rc=100)
              ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl: wait error ',‚ćēwres
              :Leave
          :EndIf
          (rc obj evt data)‚Üź4‚ÜĎwres
          :Trap 0
              :Select evt
              :Case 'Connect'
                  _buf‚Üź''
              :Case 'Block'
                  obj HandleBlock data
              :Case 'BlockLast'
                  obj HandleBlock data
              :Case 'Closed'
                  _buf‚Üź''
              :Case 'Error'
                  _buf‚Üź''
              :EndSelect
          :Else
              ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl event error:' ‚éēDMX.(EN Message)
          :EndTrap
      :EndWhile
      {}LDRC.Close'prepl'
      ‚éē‚Üź'Prepl stopped'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá obj HandleBlock data;text;idx;expr;response;id
    ‚ćĚ Buffer incoming data and process complete lines
      text‚Üź'UTF-8'‚éēUCS data
      _buf,‚Üźtext
      :While (‚éēUCS 10)‚ąä_buf
          idx‚Üź_buf‚ć≥‚éēUCS 10
          expr‚Üź(idx-1)‚ÜĎ_buf
          _buf‚Üźidx‚Üď_buf
          :If (0<‚ČĘexpr)‚ąß(‚éēUCS 13)=‚äÉ‚ĆĹexpr    ‚ćĚ Strip CR from CRLF
              expr‚Üź¬Į1‚Üďexpr
          :EndIf
          :If 0<‚ČĘexpr
              id‚ÜźExtractID expr
              response‚ÜźEval expr               ‚ćĚ ‚ćĚID: is a comment ‚ÄĒ ‚ćé ignores it
              :If 0<‚ČĘid
                  response‚Üź'(id: ''',id,''' ‚čĄ ',(1‚Üďresponse)
              :EndIf
              {}LDRC.Send obj('UTF-8'‚éēUCS response,‚éēUCS 10)
          :EndIf
      :EndWhile
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá id‚ÜźExtractID expr;pos
    ‚ćĚ Extract optional ID from trailing comment: expr ‚ćĚID:uuid
    ‚ćĚ Returns '' if no ‚ćĚID: found.
      id‚Üź''
      pos‚Üź('‚ćĚID:'‚ć∑expr)/‚ć≥‚ČĘexpr
      :If 0<‚ČĘpos
          id‚Üź((‚äÉpos)+3)‚Üďexpr
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ćĚ ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Evaluation ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźEval expr;‚éēPW;‚éēPP
      ‚éēPW‚Üź32767 ‚čĄ ‚éēPP‚Üź17
      ‚ćĚ Execute in # context. Result in #.‚ćôr (not local ‚ÄĒ Serialise
      ‚ćĚ can't resolve namespace refs held in local variables).
      :Trap 0
          :With #
              ‚ćôr‚Üź‚ćéexpr
          :EndWith
      :Else
          :If 6=‚éēDMX.EN
              r‚Üź'(tag: ''ret'')'
          :Else
              r‚ÜźErrAPLAN ‚éēDMX
          :EndIf
          ‚ÜíCLEANUP
      :EndTrap
      ‚ćĚ Serialize ‚ÄĒ three levels: APLAN, display form, literal fallback
      :Trap 0
          r‚Üź'(tag: ''ret'' ‚čĄ val: ',(ToAPLAN #.‚ćôr),')'
      :Else
          :Trap 0
              r‚Üź'(tag: ''ret'' ‚čĄ val: ',(ToAPLAN‚ćē#.‚ćôr),')'
          :Else
              r‚Üź'(tag: ''ret'')'
          :EndTrap
      :EndTrap
     CLEANUP:
      :Trap 0 ‚čĄ #.‚éēEX'‚ćôr' ‚čĄ :EndTrap
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźErrAPLAN dmx
    ‚ćĚ (tag: 'err' ‚čĄ en: 11 ‚čĄ message: 'DOMAIN ERROR' ‚čĄ dm: (...))
      r‚Üź'(tag: ''err'''
      r,‚Üź' ‚čĄ en: ',(‚ćēdmx.EN)
      r,‚Üź' ‚čĄ message: ',(ToAPLAN dmx.Message)
      r,‚Üź' ‚čĄ dm: ',(ToAPLAN dmx.DM)
      r,‚Üź')'
    ‚ąá

    ‚ćĚ ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ APLAN Serialization ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
    ‚ćĚ ‚éēSE.Dyalog.Array.Serialise ‚Üí lines, 62583‚Ć∂ ‚Üí compact single-line.

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźToAPLAN v
      r‚Üź1(62583‚Ć∂)‚éēSE.Dyalog.Array.Serialise v
      r‚Üź(r‚Č†‚éēUCS 13)/r                        ‚ćĚ Strip CR ‚ÄĒ protocol is LF-delimited
    ‚ąá

:EndNamespace
